Cell["\<\
detects valid evolution generators: either None, or a number, or an operator, \
a superoperator, or functions that generate these things.\
\>", "Text",
 InitializationCell->True,
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.464254455300824*^9, 3.464254462970779*^9}, {
  3.464255788391189*^9, 
  3.464255819881482*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"ab784248-cf41-4997-8232-\
891f18a98f54"],

Cell["\<\
Note that superoperators representing unitary evolution, such as \
RotationSuperoperator etc. are not valid generators. They are valid as events \
themselves, but not as generators of events.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.909393463623294*^9, 
  3.909393514598125*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"9b61e688-e348-4107-a58f-\
367e7da450d1"],

