Cell["\<\
This routine ensures that all ShapeFunctions and similar evolution generators \
in the event lists are put into a standard form. \
\>", "Text",
 InitializationCell->True,
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.583415884292903*^9, 
  3.583415923931601*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"c32bff12-e72a-4558-8720-\
e5f8296c550b"],

Cell["\<\
From v2.7.1b2, this routine does not implement matrix representations of \
Operators and Superoperators or check the types of operators/superoperators\
\>", "Text",
 InitializationCell->True,
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.583415928139522*^9, 
  3.583415974018056*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"82976e1c-48d1-46f0-bef8-\
a9a5c411927f"],

Cell["\<\
From v3.5.1b2m, LengthThreshold is implemented. Any arguments longer than the \
threshold are wrapped in Operator or Superoperator before standardization, in \
order to avoid long standardization loops in CombineGenerators (see bug \
MHL-351b1m-several)\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.827204658482657*^9, 3.827204725710924*^9}, {
  3.827204864664813*^9, 3.827204892987211*^9}, {3.827204952792191*^9, 
  3.827204958914624*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"eb4cd104-ff74-4d2d-b6a8-\
